plicants are invited to apply with resume and cover letter by October 15, 2024 to: susan.baer@saskhealthauthority.caManager, KM &amp; Library Services About Us The Saskatchewan Health Authority (SHA) is the largest employer in Saskatchewan, employing more than 45,000 staff in a dynamic healthcare environment. The Saskatchewan Health Authority (SHA) is committed to providing coordinated quality services that are seamless, safe and patient-centred. For more information on the city of Prince Albert please visit https://www.citypa.ca Compensation Rate of Pay: 33.44 - 35.83 Closes: 15 October, 2024 Saskatchewan Health Authority Library Regina , SK Policies and Terms of Use · jobboard@bcla.bc.ca / BCLA PO BOX 19008, Rocky Point PO, Port Moody, BC V3H 0J1 window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
